transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan Rana ji namaskar.
Executive: Haan ji namaste Ashutosh ji, main shuru thodi der se baat karu main. 
Customer: Koi nahi, koi nahi, okay fine. 
Executive: Mail kar diya tha bas maine, ye inform kar do bas. Kya mail kar diya tha?
Customer: Theek hai, mail kar diya. 
Executive: Main, haan main check kar leta hu.
Customer: Okay.
Executive: Okay, thank you, alright, thank you.
